title: game lost single handedly due to my autofilled jg who played teemo
body:
no drags. no rift. no ganks. no jg pressure. feeding. repeatedly afking in fountain for periods of time. lowest lvl in the game. lowest cs in the game. giving up and not trying.

why is auto fill in ranked? why?  do you WANT me to lose? because thats how you make people lose.
